Package: formattable
Title: Formatted Data Printing in Markdown
Version: 0.0.5.1
Authors@R: person("Kun", "Ren", , "renkun@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Print data frames with multiple types of formatting in markdown
    to improve the readability of data presented in tabular form rendered as
    web pages.
Depends: R (>= 2.14.1)
Date: 2015-04-17
Imports: htmltools, knitr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: http://renkun.me/formattable, https://github.com/renkun-ken/formattable
